否可接受的提名人選？麥美娟稱不能一概而論，但前提是要「無做反中亂港及違反《國安法》的事，亦唔好話入到議會就拉布」，希望此舉可鼓勵泛民參選。但她強調僅屬個人意願，不代表工聯會立場，內部亦未討論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"on 9, 入去幫你班PK粉色太平？"},{"pid":"285869463db70c057fee0591741089dc1df3807c","tid":2516781,"uid":53206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"而家就係要鬥紅呀屌你老母<br />\n批鬥你呢個垃圾黨"},{"pid":"e009493bcbf050a8b10c2c835c085621e8119fce","tid":2516781,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"工聯會冀為政府輸送更多<span class=\"red\"><del>人才</del></span>奴才"},{"pid":"ca01a1a5ec18e0af037d7047989cb9fe2faff2c5","tid":2516781,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"呢個女仔講得岩呀, 點解會有人唔想公開有無bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a2c801be2683f2a8548ba6d1fb5b22ac397dbf","tid":2516781,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4da3afa91a90757da2d8911e444bcdee9aec8a50","tid":2516781,"uid":248098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"泛民入到去咪又係 on 99 ，反對財政預算案，隨時被人翻卓話犯國安法既。入去等被人捉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"泛民有好多智障 ⋯"},{"pid":"fc1a0d833cd01e82f9f3e495817d4ee9eb5886ad","tid":2516781,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e584aae00e305c730bb38dbf80f0e479941afda","tid":2516781,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"提咩名0者, 自己轉形做反對派囉咪平衡到議會囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"邊個敢做 ？"},{"pid":"2c30a0beebed62b5514be93995cbf5cdea6326d3","tid":2516781,"uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08a00